Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.80,0:01:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是破忌者追击部队卡拉德小队副队长
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.22,0:01:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢克·斯塔卡特中士
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.69,0:01:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奉席翁·阿斯塔尔陛下之命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.18,0:01:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来处理掉你 莱纳·琉特
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.96,0:02:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一件事请你完成
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.01,0:02:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如陛下之命去杀掉莱纳·琉特吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.00,0:02:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.27,0:02:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗降
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.59,0:02:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.90,0:02:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.44,0:02:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敢用你那脏手 碰蜜尔可·卡拉德一根指头试试
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.72,0:02:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻送你归西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.56,0:02:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们绝不原谅对家人出手的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.86,0:02:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白的话就眨一下眼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.91,0:03:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了 释放蜜尔可·卡拉德
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.57,0:03:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟我还不想死
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.84,0:03:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在确认她平安之前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.50,0:03:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的小命就先交在我手上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.08,0:03:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是谨慎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.92,0:03:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是勇者的遗物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.67,0:03:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捡了莱纳·琉特忘记回收的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.58,0:03:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这针上伸出的线能无限伸长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.08,0:03:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且强韧不断
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.26,0:03:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.40,0:03:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据用者的手法能变为如此危险的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.73,0:03:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是罗兰德以外的国家得到了这种力量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.10,0:03:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加斯塔克吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.40,0:03:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.76,0:03:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直监视着他的旅行 你有何想法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.92,0:04:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认为莱纳·琉特对于罗兰德
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.26,0:04:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于席翁·阿斯塔尔陛下而言 真的有必要存在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.27,0:04:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无人死去 无人哭泣 和平的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.40,0:04:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妙极了 非常美好的理想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.11,0:04:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那不过是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.48,0:04:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻想而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.36,0:04:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直隐藏着实力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你离开陛下身边 无视归还的召唤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.95,0:04:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃往了国外
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.63,0:04:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就按命令来杀我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.34,0:04:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是个非常善良的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.51,0:04:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能明白蜜尔可队长为什么会喜欢上你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.14,0:04:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你死了 队长会伤心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.31,0:04:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这是我的独断
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.79,0:04:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不应该留在陛下身边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.00,0:05:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉夫拉 拉夫拉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.67,0:05:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缇亚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.74,0:05:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不太对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.19,0:05:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胜负已分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.94,0:05:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你再怎么挣扎也赢不了我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.39,0:05:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两侧有陷阱 中间没有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.64,0:05:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看穿了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.16,0:05:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你废话太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.69,0:05:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.79,0:05:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.44,0:05:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将军
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.09,0:05:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.49,0:06:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使再苟延残喘下去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.66,0:06:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这种人…已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.05,0:06:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲莉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.52,0:06:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.70,0:06:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灭了你…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.65,0:06:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.95,0:06:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底要怎样…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.17,0:06:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.31,0:06:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 你在生气吧 我道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.13,0:06:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先停一停 我请你吃团子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.96,0:06:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是更想知道 那个男人为什么要杀你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.30,0:06:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟踪我？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.71,0:06:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.51,0:06:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缇亚哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.46,0:07:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑 我挡住这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.33,0:07:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像往常一样 吃掉周围的人治好伤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天说不定能干掉我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.49,0:07:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.70,0:07:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.95,0:07:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉夫拉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.27,0:07:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加斯塔克…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.79,0:07:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布爱卡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.33,0:07:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉夫拉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.30,0:07:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳先生 请记得…约定…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.70,0:08:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复写眼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.26,0:08:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不会让你暴走的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.95,0:08:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.22,0:08:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少来碍事 区区怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.80,0:08:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挖出结晶 石喰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.52,0:08:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先是两颗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.20,0:09:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也快暴走 变成结晶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.73,0:09:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪物们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.14,0:09:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对人类绝望 悲哀的神之眼持有者们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.20,0:09:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能拯救这所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.68,0:09:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你温柔 脆弱 害怕寂寞到让人悲哀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.26,0:09:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加斯塔克！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.79,0:09:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 真够快的啊 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.82,0:09:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来兽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.60,0:09:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.54,0:09:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来多少次都没用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.30,0:09:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.11,0:10:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可真碍事 歼灭眼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.01,0:10:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾祈烧原·红莲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.03,0:10:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来兽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.57,0:10:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 不小心在结晶化前就干掉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.90,0:10:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.54,0:10:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.01,0:10:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宰了你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.94,0:10:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳 不行的 快回来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.58,0:10:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来兽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.67,0:10:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾祈雷鸣·电光…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.70,0:11:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你傻的吗 施放魔法的时候冲进来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.32,0:11:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.99,0:11:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…那么想自己去死的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.08,0:11:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就去死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.21,0:11:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你是怪物 而不是我的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.87,0:11:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就随便去消失好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.44,0:11:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你觉得不是我的搭档仆人茶友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.98,0:11:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就请便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.49,0:11:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我不会那么想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.04,0:11:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你再怎么认为自己是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.84,0:11:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你一个人也不会觉得寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.68,0:11:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都不会那么想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.03,0:11:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是目睹了一出好戏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.71,0:11:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是在童话故事里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.99,0:12:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后就应该是怪物变为了人 可喜可贺的结局呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.97,0:12:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜那家伙是怪物的事实 绝不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.15,0:12:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.62,0:12:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管他是怪物还是什么 我都不会在意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.73,0:12:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说话真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.88,0:12:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那家伙是活着就会危害世界的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.54,0:12:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你不在意 世界可不能容他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.79,0:12:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险的怪物不能留着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.44,0:12:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不管那么多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.62,0:12:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管…你居然随便说出…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.87,0:12:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.59,0:12:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.27,0:12:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以活着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.55,0:12:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 你死了 我会寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.53,0:13:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你马上就会寂寞了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.90,0:13:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他即将葬身于此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.68,0:13:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲莉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.64,0:13:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共鸣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.87,0:13:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.51,0:13:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.81,0:13:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那时候一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.79,0:13:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.69,0:13:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.92,0:13:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.14,0:13:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.56,0:13:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你渴求着 万物的破坏与消亡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.82,0:13:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.55,0:13:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生死 乐悲 全都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.37,0:14:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.66,0:14:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要反抗 那是你所期望的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.17,0:14:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论世界有多绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.00,0:14:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.57,0:14:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.91,0:14:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来终结吧 一切都随心所欲地解放
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.88,0:14:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,张开 屠戮 一切
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.51,0:14:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直至目之所及皆化为灰烬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.75,0:14:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直至目之所及皆化为灰烬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.31,0:14:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.53,0:14:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.10,0:14:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只会伤害人的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.60,0:14:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这沾满鲜血的手 触不到任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.85,0:14:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.67,0:14:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我还是想拯救 想触及
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.38,0:14:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这只手！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.10,0:14:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要还有我能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.85,0:15:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这 混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.10,0:15:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把结晶化…停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.82,0:15:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是何方神圣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.45,0:15:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.54,0:15:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.64,0:15:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉采尔之线
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.95,0:15:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是叫这名字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.76,0:15:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你的首级送回加斯塔克吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.68,0:15:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他们知道向罗兰德挑衅 会有何下场
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.21,0:15:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石喰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.84,0:15:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾祈雷鸣·电光
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.48,0:16:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缇亚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.60,0:16:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里我挡住 你带孩子们走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.45,0:16:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.06,0:16:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加斯塔克的 下次一定杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.63,0:16:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会来接你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.83,0:16:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的容身之处不是那里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.88,0:16:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑 别跑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.51,0:16:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想得手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.32,0:16:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的对手是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.52,0:16:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真背 到头来只收获了一颗结晶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.00,0:16:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「解万式者」 没想到已经出现在罗兰德
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.16,0:16:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解万式？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.17,0:16:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 你连自己的事都不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.65,0:17:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是笑话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.55,0:17:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是说勇者还没完成吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.29,0:17:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来情况大幅转变了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.09,0:17:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.46,0:17:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲莉丝快醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.82,0:17:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是轻微脑震荡 无需担心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.39,0:17:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你的确不只是个怪物…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.00,0:17:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.12,0:17:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.14,0:17:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道席翁在你走后是什么表情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.82,0:18:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真以为他是想要杀你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.19,0:18:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟那家伙 独自背负着一切在奋斗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.54,0:18:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的王和你们的王不同
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.45,0:18:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一根筋地想建立人人都能笑着生活的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.10,0:18:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个真正的笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.12,0:18:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是我自己夸大的 我还真是废啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.66,0:18:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的废柴又不是现在才有的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.28,0:18:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我觉得你们也好不了多少
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.45,0:18:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然还特地跑来追我这个没救的废柴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.25,0:18:48.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为怕伤害别人 因为怕自己受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.38,0:18:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我逃出来 孤立起自己
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.70,0:18:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我根本不可能变成一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.75,0:19:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论多么绝望 心却还是可悲地…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.78,0:19:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会回罗兰德 已经不想再逃避了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.50,0:19:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许我的力量还能派上用场
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.73,0:19:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加斯塔克也很棘手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.02,0:19:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.33,0:19:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在那之前 有一件事想拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.90,0:19:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果下次我再暴走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.92,0:19:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能杀了我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.70,0:19:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在逃避自己是怪物的事实
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.96,0:19:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是在害怕 总担心有天会杀了你们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.73,0:19:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 希望你给予我勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.55,0:19:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇气？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.10,0:19:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我能够不逃避 战斗到最后的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.23,0:19:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这样你就能回来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.85,0:19:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.58,0:20:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳·琉特似乎会主动返回罗兰德
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.03,0:20:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此外 大陆各地相当数量的魔眼持有者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.06,0:20:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在组建反加斯塔克势力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.07,0:20:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后可以考虑以莱纳·琉特作为桥梁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.42,0:20:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结成反加斯塔克战线这一选择
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.48,0:20:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些东西没有任何意义
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.63,0:20:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论莱纳有多大帮助 抑或一无用处
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.37,0:20:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都没有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.25,0:20:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实卢克·斯塔卡特能杀掉莱纳·琉特的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.50,0:20:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而对你来说更好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.93,0:20:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你才发出了那种命令书吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.66,0:20:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.86,0:20:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会杀莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.67,0:20:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不杀莱纳·琉特？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.25,0:21:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.68,0:21:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是选择最残酷的一条道路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.20,0:21:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒觉得正因莱纳是你重要的友人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.71,0:21:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才更应该趁早杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.43,0:21:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这样真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.71,0:21:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它杀掉的话 立刻就会产生变革
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.60,0:21:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它和你一样 都是世界的齿轮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.62,0:21:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话就不用牺牲朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.25,0:21:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只沿正确的道路前进
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.07,0:21:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必要时敢于粉碎一切重要之物的坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.70,0:21:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粉碎友人 爱人 这一切
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.09,0:21:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你唯一的资质
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.80,0:21:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但愿你不会后悔 我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.79,0:21:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的勇者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.99,0:23:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦事我不会再做
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.34,0:23:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是这么说过 但凡事也该有个度吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.48,0:23:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一堆活是怎么回事 席翁你是魔鬼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.41,0:23:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 果然不该回来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.13,0:23:44.99,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗兰德之暗
